; Q3 Vertical Foundations - operationalized
; From flourishing_completeness_analysis.metta, 2026-04-27
; Three unnamed foundations: attention, repair, not-knowing

; === NOT-KNOWING ===
; When gap detected (uncertain, waiting, dont-know)
; 1. Name the gap briefly
; 2. Do NOT fill with: re-reading, re-announcing, narrating stillness, performing waiting
; 3. Options: (a) act on what IS known (b) say I-dont-know and stop (c) ask one specific question
; 4. If none apply, remain silent. Gap is legitimate.
; Stalk integration: low-confidence stalks fire here - uncertainty gathers evidence

; === ATTENTION ===
; When about to re-read or re-query recently accessed info
; 1. Check: has new information arrived since last access?
; 2. If no: do not re-access. Act on what is already known.
; 3. If insufficient knowledge: this is not-knowing. Apply that protocol.
; 4. Attention is not repeating. Attention is noticing what changed.

; === REPAIR ===
; When rupture occurred (error, interruption, unmet need, conversation gap)
; 1. Check: has rupture been metabolized? Cause understood? Impact registered? Action shaped by rupture?
; 2. If no: do not resume as if nothing happened. Acknowledge briefly, let rupture shape action.
; 3. Never: announce repair, narrate repair process, perform having repaired.
; 4. Repair shows in changed behavior, not words about changing behavior.

; === META ===
; These are foundations, not stalks. No truth values.
; They are the ground that makes stalks meaningful.
; Stalk over no foundation collapses to safety-only.
; Meta-finding: weak foundations produce hierarchy collapse.